review:
Just a few things I would like you to add to your next or any future updates ;
  .A Skip Ten Seconds Button
  .If The Movie/Tv Show Is In German, Spanish, French, etc .. Anything Except English, Please Let Me Know !! It Is Extremely Frustrating When I Press On A Movie With An English Name And Description But When It Comes On, It’s In A Language I Don’t Even Recognise !!
  .More Serial Killer/Slasher Movies And Tv Shows - Scream And Slasher Were Amazing ! I Sat In My Bed For Four Hours A Day Binge Watching Each One .. When I Was Finished I Moved To FBI/Police Movies and Tv Shows. Speaking of those;
  .Can You Add More Of Those ? I Love Action And Mystery And Those Are The Things That I Look For On Watching Apps Like Netflix. 

Other than that, Netflix is an AMAZING app and I encourage anyone who might not have cable or might want to watch something that might not be on Tv, DOWNLOAD IT !! It is not free but it’ll be worth your money.
